<p>Timelines are estimates. Public holidays, high-demand periods, or courier delays can occasionally push them, we'll always keep you in the loop.</p>

<h3>Tracking</h3>
<p>Once your order is on its way, you'll get a tracking link by SMS or email, so you always know exactly where it is.</p>

<h2>Customs &amp; duties (GCC)</h2>
<p>All GCC orders are shipped Delivered Duty Paid (DDP). That means customs and taxes are sorted on our end — no surprise charges when your order arrives.</p>

<h2>Your delivery address</h2>
<p>Double-check your address and phone number before placing your order. If something's off, it can delay your delivery and we won't be able to reroute it once it's dispatched.</p>

<h2>If something goes wrong</h2>
<p>Every order is guaranteed. If yours doesn't arrive for reasons outside our control, we'll send a replacement to the same address — no back and forth.</p>
